Add a touch of olive oil to pan until hot
Add in steak for 4 minutes and
Crush a bit of @garlic to the pan
Add some @thyme to the pan
Add more olive oil
Add @butter and baste steak
Flip steak and cook for another 4 minutes
Cook until meat feels like at top of wrist above wrist strap. rare is left of the palm, medium is at wrist strap,
